        <name>Accounts_Email_Body</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hi,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Please follow this &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;{!Accounts_Report_Link}&quot;&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; to find the Accounts that were recently assigned to you.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Please be aware that you are the current owner of these &lt;b&gt;Accounts, Opps, and Contacts&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
You can assign them to another team member, by reaching out to SalesOps with the list of the records and the new owner&apos;s full name.</text>
    </textTemplates>
