        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hi,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Please note that {!Loop_on_Meetings.previousOwnerName}&apos;s open meetings have been assigned to you since their user is now inactive.&lt;br&gt;
Please follow this &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;{!Meetings_Report_Link}&quot;&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; to find the Meetings that were assigned to you.&lt;br&gt;
You are the current owner of these &lt;b&gt;Meetings&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;u&gt;Time is of essence!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Note that some of these meetings may be taking place in the next days. Please review them ASAP and assign them to another team member to take the meeting.&lt;br&gt;
If any help is required, please reach out to salesops@similarweb.com</text>
