        <name>Territories_Email_Body</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>true</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>Hi,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Note that {!Loop_on_Territories.previousOwnerName}&apos;s Territories have been assigned to you since their user is now inactive.&lt;br&gt;
Territory ownership means that &lt;b&gt;all the accounts in the territory&lt;/b&gt; will move to &lt;b&gt;your ownership.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Please follow this &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;{!Territories_Report_Link}&quot;&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; to find the Territories that were assigned to you.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;b&gt;This is only an interim solution -  managers should not be territories owners.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Please work with the growth team to reassign to a relevant team member.&lt;br&gt;
